public class HistoryquoteExchangeSet<S extends Securitycurrency<S>> extends Object
Tracks instruments during GTNet historyquote exchange, maintaining state of which have been filled. This helper class manages the intersection of BaseHistoryquoteThru instruments with GTNet-enabled instruments and tracks which ones have received historical quotes from remote servers. It supports:
  • Building the initial set from SecurityCurrencyMaxHistoryquoteData
  • Creating request DTOs with date ranges
  • Marking instruments as filled when historyquotes are received
  • Tracking "want to receive" markers from suppliers for push-back
  • Returning unfilled instruments for fallback to connectors
